  "name": "Mighty Ambush",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/feats/deceitful.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per round, when the vigilante succeeds at a hidden strike, he can instantly drop the damaged enemy unconscious for 1d4 rounds. A successful Fortitude saving throw negates this effect (DC = 10 + 1/2 the vigilante’s class level + the higher of the vigilante’s Strength and Dexterity modifiers). Whether or not a creature’s saving throw is successful, it can’t be affected by that vigilante’s mighty ambush again for 24 hours.</p>\n<p>Only a stalker vigilante of at least 10th level can select this talent.</p>",
